quran[86]{c,v,t}:
  78,1,Kodi akufunsana nkhani zotani
  78,2,Ali kufunsana za nkhani ija yaikulu
  78,3,Nkhani imene akusiyana maganizo pakati pawo
  78,4,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwa"
  78,5,"Iyayi, iwo adzadziwa posachedwapa"
  78,6,Kodi Ife sitidapange dziko lapansi monga ngati kama
  78,7,Ndi mapiri ngati zikhomo
  78,8,Ndipo Ife tidakulengani inu awiri awiri
  78,9,Ndipo tidapanga tulo kukhala ngati mpumulo wanu
  78,10,Ndipo tidapanga usiku kukhala chophimba
  78,11,Ndipo tinapanga usana kukhala kopezera zofuna zanu
  78,12,Ndipo tidamanga mlengalenga miyamba isanu ndi iwiri
  78,13,Ndipo tidakhazikitsa mmenemo nyali yowala
  78,14,Ndipo tidatumiza mvula yambiri kuchokera ku mitambo ya mvula
  78,15,Kuti timeretse chakudya ndi mbewu
  78,16,Ndipo minda ya zomera zothinana
  78,17,Ndithudi tsiku la chiweruzo lidakhazikitsidwa kale
  78,18,Tsiku limene lipenga lidzalira ndipo inu mudzadza mu magulumagulu
  78,19,Ndipomumlengalengamudzatsegulidwa ndipo mudzakhala ngati makomo
  78,20,Ndipo mapiri onse adzayendetsedwa ndi kukhala ngati nthunzi yamadzi
  78,21,Ndithudi Gahena ili kuwayembekezera
  78,22,Mudzi wa anthu ophwanya malamulo
  78,23,Kumeneko ndiko kumene adzakhale mpaka kalekale
  78,24,Kumeneko sadzalawa chozizira kapena kumwa china chilichonse
  78,25,"Kupatula Al-Naba\t637 madzi owira ndi mafinya"
  78,26,Mphotho yoyeneradi
  78,27,"Chifukwa, ndithudi, iwo sanali kuopa chidzudzulo chathu"
  78,28,Ndipo iwo moyerekedwa anali kukana chivumbulutso chathu
  78,29,Ndipo Ife tidalemba m’Buku zonse zimene anali kuchita
  78,30,Motero inu lawani! Inu simudzalandira china chilichonse koma manzunzo ochuluka
  78,31,Ndithudi kwa anthu oopa Mulungu kudzakhala kupambana
  78,32,Minda ndi m’minda ya mphesa
  78,33,Ndi a namwali akulu akulu ofanana zaka
  78,34,Ndi chikho chodzadza
  78,35,Kumeneko iwo sadzamva mawu opanda pake kapena nkhani zabodza
  78,36,Imeneyi ndiyo mphotho yochokera kwa Ambuye wako ndipo ndi mphotho yokwanira
  78,37,"Ambuye wa Kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndi zonse zimene zili pakati pawo, Mwini chisoni chosatha ndipo iwo sadzatha kulankhula naye"
  78,38,Patsiku limene Mzimu ndi angelo adzaima pa mizere ndipo palibe amene adzalankhula kupatula yekhayo amene adzalandira chilolezo cha Mwini chifundo chosatha ndipo adzanena chinthu chimene chili choona
  78,39,"Ndithudi tsiku limeneli ndi loona, motero iye amene afuna, mulekeni atsatire njira yobwerera kwa Ambuye wake"
  78,40,"Ndithudi takuchenjezani za chilango chowawa chimene chili nkudza posachedwa. Tsiku limene munthu adzayang’ana ntchito zimene manja ake adatsogoza, ndipo osakhulupirira adzati: “Kalanga ine, ndikanakhala dothi.”"
  79,1,Pali iwo amene amalanda mwankhanza
  79,2,Ndi pali iwo amene amachotsa mwaufulu
  79,3,Ndi pali iwo amene amauluka
  79,4,Ndi pali iwo amene amathamanga ngati ali pa liwiro loopsya
  79,5,Ndi pali angelo amene amakwaniritsa kuchita malamulo a Ambuye wawo
  79,6,Patsiku limene dziko ndi mapiri zidzagwedezeka kwambiri
  79,7,Ndi kulira kwa lipenga kawiri
  79,8,"Mitima, patsiku limeneli, idzafumuka ndi kuda nkhawa"
  79,9,Maso awo atagwetsa pansi
  79,10,"Iwo amanena kuti: “Kodi ife tidzabwerera monga momwe tinali poyamba?”"
  79,11,“Angakhale mafupa athu ataola?”
  79,12,"Iwo amati: “Kubwerera kotero ndi kopanda phindu.”"
  79,13,Koma udzakhala mfuwu umodzi okha
  79,14,"Pamene, taona, iwo adzadzipeza okha ali pamwamba pa nthaka ali ndi moyo"
  79,15,Kodiinumudaimvankhaniya Mose
  79,16,PameneAmbuye wake adamuitana mu dambo lodalitsika la Tuwa
  79,17,“Pita kwa Farao; Ndithudi iye waphwanya malamulo mopyola muyezo.”
  79,18,"“Ndipo ukamuuze kuti: Kodi ungadziyeretse wekha?”"
  79,19,“Ndi kuti ine ndikulondolere kwa Ambuye wako kuti uzimuopa Iye?”
  79,20,Kotero iye adamuonetsa chizindikiro cha chikulu
  79,21,Koma iye adachikana ndipo sanamvere
  79,22,Iye adapitirizabe kuchita zoipa
  79,23,Ndipo iye adaitana anthu ake onse ndipo anafuula mokweza
  79,24,"Nati: “Ine ndine Ambuye wanu wapamwamba mwamba.” Al-Naziat"
  79,25,Motero Mulungu adamugwetsera iye chilango chifukwa cha mau ake omaliza ndi oyamba
  79,26,Ndithudi mu izi muli phunziro lomveka kwa anthu oopa Mulungu
  79,27,Kodi inu ndinu ovuta kulenga kapena thambo la mlengalenga limene Mulungu adalilenga
  79,28,Iye analikweza m’mwamba ndi kulikonza bwino
  79,29,Usiku wake amaukuta ndi m’dima ndipo masana ake amatulutsa kuwala
  79,30,Ndipo pambuyo pake adalikulitsa dziko
  79,31,Ndipo anatulutsa madzi ndi msipu
  79,32,Ndipo adazika mapiri molimbika
  79,33,Chakudya cha phindu kwa inu ndi kwa zoweta zanu
  79,34,Koma pamene mavuto akulu akudza
  79,35,Tsiku limene munthu adzayamba kuganiza ntchito zake zonse
  79,36,Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi kuti aliyense aione
  79,37,Ndipo kwa iye ophwanya malamulo
  79,38,Ndipo anasankha moyo wapadziko lino
  79,39,Ndithudi malo ake okhala ndi ku Gahena
  79,40,Koma kwa iwo amene amaopa kukaima pamaso pa Ambuye wake ndi machimo ndipo anali kudziletsa kuchita chifuniro chopanda pake
  79,41,Ndithudi adzakhala ku Paradiso
  79,42,Amakufunsa za nthawi imene chigumula chidzabwere
  79,43,Iwe siudziwa zoti unene china chili chonse
  79,44,Ndi Ambuye wako yekha amene amadziwa tsiku
  79,45,Iwe ndiwe mchenjezi chabe kwa iwo amene ali kuliopa tsikuli
  79,46,"Patsiku limene iwo adzachiona chigumula, kudzakhala ngati kuti iwo sanakhale padziko lapansi nthawi yaitali koma usiku umodzi kapena usana wokha"